snippet.title: Judge Says NO To AMBER HEARD Sanctions In JOHNNY DEPP Trial
snippet.description:
Great news! The Judge says no to Amber Heard and her sanctions in the Johnny Depp trial.

Amber Heard put forward a whole bunch of sanctions against Johnny Depp for the exclusion of evidence from the trial. No the judge has said no and denied the motions and sanctions against Johnny Depp.

Document - https://www.fairfaxcounty.gov/circuit/sites/circuit/files/assets/documents/pdf/high-profile/depp%20v%20heard/cl-2019-2911-order-sanctions-mot-in-limine-9-25-2020.pdf
